wp-content/uploads/2011/03/taxcaster-lite-plugin-shortcode.png\" rel=\"shadowbox[post-5835];player=img;\"><img src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/taxcaster-lite-plugin-shortcode-300x92.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"taxcaster-lite-plugin-shortcode\" width=\"300\" height=\"92\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-5838\" /></a>TurboTax came to WebDevStudios for our experience in <a href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wordpress/plugins/\" title=\"Custom WordPress Plugin Programmers\">developing custom WordPress plugins</a>.  The new TaxCaster plugin couldn&#8217;t be easier to use.  The TaxCaster app is powered by a shortcode, so it can be easily added to any post or page and the application will automatically be displayed on your site!</p>\n<p>Below is the TaxCaster application in action:</p>\n<object width=\"450\" height=\"550\">\n	    <param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/plugins/taxcaster/includes/EightQuestionRefundEstimator.swf\">\n	    <embed src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/plugins/taxcaster/includes/EightQuestionRefundEstimator.swf\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\">\n	    </embed>\n	</object><p>Powered by <a href=\"http://turbotax.intuit.com/personal-taxes/online/free-edition.jsp\">Turbo Tax Software</a></p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/taxcaster/\" target=\"_blank\">download the TaxCaster WordPress plugin</a> from the WordPress.org Plugin Directory.  This plugin supports all current versions of WordPress including Multisite!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2011/03/24/turbotax-releases-taxcaster-wordpress-plugin/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";