2010/12/collabpress-logo-300x84.png\" rel=\"shadowbox[post-3633];player=img;\"></a>WebDevstudios is proud to <a href=\"http://collabpress.org/blog/2010/11/collabpress-v1-0-final-has-been-released/\" target=\"_blank\">announce the release</a> of CollabPress 1.0!  For those of you who are not familiar with <a href=\"http://collabpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\">CollabPress</a>, it is an all in one project and task management plugin for WordPress.  It allows you to transform your standard WP installation into a full featured project management application in a single click!  Using CollabPress on your WordPress website allows you to easily create unlimited projects, task lists, and tasks with all of the features you would expect.</p>\n<p>Some of the great features CollabPress 1.0 offers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Unlimited projects, task lists, tasks, and comments</li>\n<li>Easily edit/delete projects, task lists, tasks, and comments</li>\n<li>Email notifications for new tasks and comments</li>\n<li>Task due dates with a calendar view</li>\n<li>Uses built-in WordPress user accounts</li>\n<li>Activity log tracking all activity</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We are also working on releasing additional features for CollabPress 1.0 so be sure to <a href=\"http://collabpress.org/stay-informed/\" target=\"_blank\">sign up</a> for our newsletter or <a href=\"http://twitter.com/collabpress\" target=\"_blank\">follow us</a> on Twitter for updates and information.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://collabpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> for more information on CollabPress, to visit our CollabPress support forum or to download CollabPress for WordPress today!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2010/12/08/collabpress-1-0-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_bas