ient does not have the right to define family to include a same-sex partner.</strong>','144.651','','publish','closed','closed','','144-651','','','2011-03-26 21:27:21','2011-03-27 02:27:21','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?post_type=statutes&p=136',0,'statutes','',0),(137,4,'2011-03-26 20:07:45','2011-03-27 01:07:45','The straight spouse of a volunteer firefighter can transfer their deceased spouse’s pension to their account. <strong>A same-sex partner does not have the authority to change the election.</strong>','424A.02','','publish','closed','closed','','424a-02','','','2011-03-26 21:26:41','2011-03-27 02:26:41','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?post_type=statutes&p=137',0,'statutes','',0),(138,4,'2011-03-26 20:09:11','2011-03-27 01:09:11','A surviving straight spouse is entitled to sue for wrongful death. <strong>The same-sex partner of a decedent does not have standing to bring a similar claim.</strong>','466.05','','publish','closed','closed','','466-05','','','2011-03-26 21:25:45','2011-03-27 02:25:45','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?post_type=statutes&p=138',0,'statutes','',0),(139,4,'2011-03-26 20:10:50','2011-03-27 01:10:50','An individual cannot be compelled to testify against their spouse in court. <strong>There is no similar protection for same-sex partners.</strong>','595.02','','publish','closed','closed','','595-02','','','2011-03-26 23:29:30','2011-03-27 04:29:30','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?post_type=statutes&p=139',0,'statutes','',0),(140,4,'2011-03-26 20:10:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2011-03-26 20:10:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?post_type=statutes&p=140',0,'statutes','',0),(141,7,'2011-03-26 20:13:27','2011-03-27 01:13:27','TO ENSURE THAT SAME-SEX COUPLES AND THEIR FAMILIES HAVE EQUAL RIGHTS AND CONSIDERATIONS UNDER MINNESOTA LAW.','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2011-03-26 22:06:24','2011-03-27 03:06:24','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?page_id=141',0,'page','',0),(142,7,'2011-03-26 20:13:25','2