ller. “I’m his sister. You should call his partner.” But the office refused.\r\n\r\n“As Richard’s sister, I was shocked by the unfairness and lack of respect for their relationship,” Marg said. “My family shouldn’t be treated unfairly – especially during such a difficult time.”','Fairness and Respect Are Needed Especially During Difficult Times','','inherit','open','open','','236-revision-4','','','2011-03-27 03:14:22','2011-03-27 08:14:22','',236,'http://fcw.lan/2011/03/27/236-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(308,4,'2011-03-27 03:14:04','2011-03-27 08:14:04','Please join Project 515 for a fantastic Spring Fundraiser on Wednesday, March 30 from 6pm-8pm. The event will be co-hosted by Jason Bright and Alex Matusevich and held at their beautiful home in Minneapolis. Suggested minimum donation of $51.50 per person. \r\n\r\nAppetizers and beverages will be provided.\r\n\r\n2100 West Lake of the Isles Parkway\r\nMinneapolis, MN 55405\r\n\r\nPlease RSVP here, call (612) 246-3885, or email info@project515.org by March 23.','Project 515 Spring 2011 Fundraiser','','inherit','open','open','','298-revision-2','','','2011-03-27 03:14:04','2011-03-27 08:14:04','',298,'http://fcw.lan/2011/03/27/298-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(309,4,'2011-03-27 03:15:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2011-03-27 03:15:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://fcw.lan/?p=309',0,'post','',0),(310,8,'2011-03-27 03:15:47','2011-03-27 08:15:47','Women holding hands','75403720_47','','inherit','open','open','','75403720_47','','','2011-03-27 03:15:47','2011-03-27 08:15:47','',239,'http://fcw.lan/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/75403720_47.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(311,8,'2011-03-27 01:56:09','2011-03-27 06:56:09','Jane’s partner, Carol, was diagnosed with a terminal illness late in 2004. By the time the disease had progressed to the point that Carol required full-time care, she had already spent most of her assets on medical bills. Carol applied 