ping us in one or more of the following ways:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Phone-tree activism</li>\r\n	<li>Host a house party</li>\r\n	<li>Join our Speaker\'s Bureau</li>\r\n	<li>Assist with tabling at events</li>\r\n	<li>Share your story</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you are ready to get involved and support our mission, please fill out our volunteer interest form and tell us how you’d like to help. Please complete the following form if you have any questions:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Participate','','inherit','open','open','','67-revision-5','','','2011-03-27 04:26:15','2011-03-27 09:26:15','',67,'http://fcw.lan/2011/03/27/67-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(378,4,'2011-03-26 19:41:59','2011-03-27 00:41:59','','Volunteer Opportunities','','inherit','open','open','','89-revision-3','','','2011-03-26 19:41:59','2011-03-27 00:41:59','',89,'http://fcw.lan/2011/03/26/89-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(380,8,'2011-03-27 04:35:05','2011-03-27 09:35:05','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://fcw.lan/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/almeida-Christine.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-366 alignleft\" title=\"almeida, Christine\" src=\"http://fcw.lan/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/almeida-Christine.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"123\" /></a><strong>Cristine Almeida, Secretary </strong>\r\nCristine is an attorney and owns her own public affairs consulting company, representing corporations, trade associations and non-profit organizations before state legislatures, local governments and regulatory agencies. She has also been active in politics and public policy for 18 years. She was chief of staff to Minnesota DFL Senate Majority Leader Dean E. Johnson in 2004-2005, and prior to that was an attorney in private practice. She has also worked on numerous statewide and local campaigns, both as paid staff and as a volunteer. She was a senior advisor to the winning Clean Water, Land and Legacy Campaign in 2008, was a delegate to the Democratic National Convention in August 2008, and was active in Latinos for Obama. Sh